{"tid":1541703,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【公告】 2047年 中華人民共和國 - 香港直轄市","createTime":"2019-09-04T15:41:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T15:51:40.000Z","uid":135762,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"640a7af79817ef85f08f49b63348642a6691da6d","tid":1541703,"uid":135762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T15:41:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">2047年<br />\n中英聯合聲明正式完結（雖然而家已「被成」歷史文件）<br />\n香港將會成為中共直轄市<br />\n高度自治 港人治港 一國兩制<br />\n將不復存在<br />\n香港完全失去其根本價值<br />\n從事各行各業的巴打絲打<br />\n<br />\n你們確保工作不會被更底價的奴工搶奪？<br />\n你們有辦法技術轉型嗎？<br />\n你們確保年中不會失業？<br />\n你們確保你們的資產不會被凍結？<br />\n你們確保不會被秋後算帳？<br />\n你們想將人生的收成期被極權收割？<br />\n你們想子女成為中共的奴隸？<br />\n你們想子女說<br />\n「屌你老母爛臭閪」或是<br />\n「操你妈B」<br />\n<br />\n</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">當一隻會生金蛋的母雞死亡<br />\n她將永遠失去其價值</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>還是金蛋會孵化出會生金蛋的母雞</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">接下來呢半年<br />\n可能會好攰<br />\n但係各位要清楚<br />\n中共內憂外患<br />\n堅持 越拖越耐<br />\n距離我哋嘅勝利就越近<br />\n<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">貿易戰 特朗普助攻<br />\n數千萬名低技術中國工人會失業</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: maroon;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">長江三峽大霸 變形  倘若堤壩倒塌<br />\n將有500,000,000受災害</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">中國糧食不足<br />\n大部份農田荒廢 被工業污染<br />\n存在第二次大饑荒可能性</span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">條例動議撤回<br />\n令中国人覺得反抗的可能性</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">全球各國正感受到中共納粹的氣氛 第二個蘇聯崛起 洗腦式滲透</span></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求<br />\n缺一不可</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n勝利在望<br />\n香港未來<br />\n係我哋呢一代嘅"},{"pid":"49d7d637da4b3499ded476465a560b3b0ea73bf0","tid":1541703,"uid":226569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T15:43:16.000Z","msg":"now or never <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBritish National (Overseas) Citizens should be given full British Citizenship.<br />\n<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2F244402&d=aWTYmjKPTw65bzRUwiqYJAogPkW5zMkxdNnzPoGklno%3D&h=b5a19c95\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402</a>"},{"pid":"415a164121a609143de257ac58feea6458a7fd08","tid":1541703,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T15:47:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">撤LLM 對準政權</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3E7OjKb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3E7OjKb.gif&h=66b4ea40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zNutjAi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzNutjAi.jpg&h=1817afe5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">得到黨媒認證</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sELTeyX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsELTeyX.png&h=0e8c0efe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">#Chinazi旗係一個符號，不斷向世界輸出反共思想！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">#Chinazi 赤納粹</span></span></strong><br />\nChinazi就係China+Nazi。<br />\n赤=共產紅色恐怖, 納粹不解釋。<